  "body": "<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HKphpcF.png\" alt=\"Plushie Mod\" width=\"856\" height=\"112\" /></h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Adds lots of cute Minecraft Plushies to the game!</em></h1>\n<p><br /> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bQC6j31.png\" alt=\"Plushies\" width=\"841\" height=\"442\" /><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><em><br /></em></span></p>\n<hr />\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 36px;\">Important:</span></strong></em><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><em><br /></em></span></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">v1.3 upwards requires the Architectury API!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">For Fabric, you'll also need the Fabric API!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Please help us translate the mod right <a href=\"https://gist.github.com/Link4real/c465b77b9dd02802ca35197f6db3500b\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">This mod will receive updates in the future.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong>Please note:</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><em>NOT AN OFFICIAL MINECRAFT PRODUCT.</em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><em>NOT APPROVED BY OR ASSOCIATED WITH MOJANG OR MICROSOFT</em></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\"><img style=\"text-align: center;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LMC7eqB.png\" alt=\"Plushie Mod 3D\" width=\"364\" height=\"205\" /><br /></span></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-size: 36px;\"><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/Link4real/af545420163c11858c4f4640b00191cd\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3L7vkvu.png\" alt=\"Github Gist Link\" width=\"310\" height=\"104\" /></a></span></h1>",
